 te the deployment of ONAP on OpenStack\, with ONAP services being deployed
  on top of Kubernetes as microservices.\nIncluding how to deploy K8S on Op
 enstack by provisioning a Kubernetes Cluster which consists of Master & N
 odes enabling TOSCA modeling of ONAP applications as native K8S micro-se
 rvices using K8S templates to deploy ONAP workloads.
