 ngsten Fabric in the future. It also proposed a reference implementation o
 f the security engine policy called Moon hosted by the OPNFV community.\nO
 range as major Telco operator is planning the deployment in production of 
 this “external PDP mechanism” in 2019 for its first VNFs\, in collabor
 ation with the upstream community and Red Hat.
